<h1>{{ title }}</h1>

<p>I'm an expat living in Hong Kong with my wife for some time. I've worked in public relations, edited a business travel magazine,ran a graphic design studio, and taught English as a foreign language at several universities, both in the US and China. Not necessarily in that order. </p>

<p>What began as a simple way of keeping track of what my small book club (and me on the sly) expanded out into other books I've read and enjoyed. If I don't like a book that much, it is not recorded.  </p>

<p>The creative brief for this site: I wanted simplicity. Security. Files as app, so I wouldn't be locked into a database. I found 11ty (eleventy) as someone who rarely codes, fit the bill. It just works.   </p>

<p>If you have any questions, comments, or suggestions, please don't hesitate to reach out to me at davidrosshk@gmail.com.</p>